Installed-Size: Gimp 31 Mo + GTK 26.3 Mo
Description: GIMP is an acronym for GNU Image Manipulation Program. It is a 
freely distributed program for such tasks as photo retouching, image composition
and image authoring.GTK is a library to build graphical user interfaces (GUIs) 
originally for X Window
